{"tid":768968,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"委內瑞拉總統受襲","createTime":"2018-08-06T00:01:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-06T00:27:22.000Z","uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ea726b3726d9684c37b2bd4ebfa32bd5072699b9","tid":768968,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T00:01:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1718714/org/9f63c0b8737873a529ddc05cdaf32aa4.jpg/S59lVJGOxmLZvYimJHcZX3fehX8acrL6hLkFsIS5BbA?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1718714%2Forg%2F9f63c0b8737873a529ddc05cdaf32aa4.jpg%2FS59lVJGOxmLZvYimJHcZX3fehX8acrL6hLkFsIS5BbA%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=e21af67d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1718690/org/91fbd829cf342466050f5e402af88700.JPG/cYfNU1PmJRV3l0Ei45KEQcMQTdH7F72Lu6JRRruiUUY?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1718690%2Forg%2F91fbd829cf342466050f5e402af88700.JPG%2FcYfNU1PmJRV3l0Ei45KEQcMQTdH7F72Lu6JRRruiUUY%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=59d65c1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n馬杜羅出席玻利瓦爾國民警衛隊成立81周年的慶祝活動，在他演說期間，傳出爆炸聲響，站於講台上、身穿白色格仔套裝的總統夫人弗洛雷斯（Cilia Flores）露出一個驚訝的表情。（美聯社）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1718688/org/121a5bf196a6df1188d6e953e17e3aa8.jpg/5b1IavVcrXZEUYk1z1-fV3uPrv4DfvlqR3oRAUd6EQE?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1718688%2Forg%2F121a5bf196a6df1188d6e953e17e3aa8.jpg%2F5b1IavVcrXZEUYk1z1-fV3uPrv4DfvlqR3oRAUd6EQE%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=d0c42506&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n爆炸聲響傳出後，電視直播的鏡頭跳到軍隊列隊站立的畫面。（美聯社）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1718689/org/68bc8d261c7c3fb6f9809ea710b7d294.JPG/d6rwN57NSzBXWIcAuFrYpZNFIbvpEQ2lbGwhC2xsIQs?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1718689%2Forg%2F68bc8d261c7c3fb6f9809ea710b7d294.JPG%2Fd6rwN57NSzBXWIcAuFrYpZNFIbvpEQ2lbGwhC2xsIQs%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=7f3fc1b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鏡頭下的軍人不久亦四散逃跑。（美聯社）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1718691/org/efafb1e7d83cf78863a08bf17d8f8c20.jpg/qiwnIaFUr4aDISaIRzFJMTEXh15kncQ_x7EpZsexKWY?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1718691%2Forg%2Fefafb1e7d83cf78863a08bf17d8f8c20.jpg%2FqiwnIaFUr4aDISaIRzFJMTEXh15kncQ_x7EpZsexKWY%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=9fa9865e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在另一邊廂，安保人員衝向枱上的總統。（美聯社）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1718693/org/f09cad635b843b56dd990a708e2c1f46.jpg/HmVhtS-6sAbgDDmMgAH7dyfWAiF0zBKBbZQYt22UGLc?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1718693%2Forg%2Ff09cad635b843b56dd990a708e2c1f46.jpg%2FHmVhtS-6sAbgDDmMgAH7dyfWAiF0zBKBbZQYt22UGLc%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=8f09a1ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n保安人員舉起了數張疑似是防彈的黑色長方形盾牌。（美聯社）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1718694/org/9c559dde8d0800998d3c71fdd7a6d5b6.jpg/cyeGdgAgKUV-Kh-uD0WpgcBRQYfu15EPSZU-O0mVPjs?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1718694%2Forg%2F9c559dde8d0800998d3c71fdd7a6d5b6.jpg%2FcyeGdgAgKUV-Kh-uD0WpgcBRQYfu15EPSZU-O0mVPjs%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=de6d885b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n總統被保安人員從從包圍。（美聯社）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1718692/org/96c6df130686bc24c982b694745b7b8b.jpg/qY-3LABgZ7ckoc_HfYnI1fDNJkLCueOMBy0G3ActBtw?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1718692%2Forg%2F96c6df130686bc24c982b694745b7b8b.jpg%2FqY-3LABgZ7ckoc_HfYnI1fDNJkLCueOMBy0G3ActBtw%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=95934e0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有軍人頭與臉披血。有數人攙扶着他。（美聯社）<br />\n<br />\n委内瑞拉總統馬杜羅周六（4日）出席軍方活動，在他演說期間傳出爆炸聲響，電視直播的鏡頭震動了一下，站於講台上的馬杜羅妻子弗洛雷斯（Cilia Flores）露出一個驚訝的表情，直播鏡頭隨即跳到軍隊列隊站立的畫面，究竟當時實際情況如何？<br />\n<br />\n馬杜羅周六出席玻利瓦爾國民警衛隊成立81周年的慶祝活動，從當時電視直播鏡頭所見，原本在台上滔滔不絕發表演說的馬杜羅突然停頓，台上的總統夫人弗洛雷斯（Cilia Flores）、數名軍官與他抬頭望向上方，鏡頭隨即轉到軍人列隊的畫面，不過軍人不久亦四散逃跑，直播隨即中斷。<br />\n<br />\n從《今日俄羅斯》的現場片段可見，爆炸聲傳出後，安保人員衝向總統，把他包圍，並舉起了數張疑似是防彈的黑色長方形「盾牌」。<br />\n<br />\n委內瑞拉新聞局局長羅德里格斯（Jorge Rodriguez）指襲擊是下午5時41分發生，有爆炸物的無人機飛近演說場地爆炸，他甚至指看到一個飛行裝置在他眼前爆炸。他指事件針對馬杜羅，有7名國家衛兵受傷，從新華社圖片可見有軍人頭與臉披血，要由數人扶着。<br />\n<br />\n究竟事件是由何人策劃？馬杜羅指有證據顯示，事件與哥倫比亞及美國佛羅里達州有關，那兒有流亡海外的委內瑞拉人居住，他又指總統桑托斯（Juan Manuel Santos）亦要為事件負責，已經逮捕了數名策劃者。<br />\n<br />\n惟美聯社報道，3名身處爆炸現場的消防員與官方的說法不一，他們指在馬杜羅演說地點附近一橦住宅大廈發生爆炸，有黑煙從大廈窗戶冒出。<br />\n<br />\n美聯社亦報道，組織Soldiers in T-shirts承認策劃襲擊，組織在twitter指，周六計劃操控兩架載住爆炸物的無人機飛向馬杜羅，但在飛機接觸目標人物之前，政府士兵已經把無人機擊落，報道指未能核實消息。<br />\n<br />\n（美聯社／路透社／今日俄羅斯）<br />\n撰文：高紫恩<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/219036/%E5%A4%9A%E5%9C%96-%E5%A7%94%E5%85%A7%E7%91%9E%E6%8B%89%E7%B8%BD%E7%B5%B1%E5%8F%97%E8%A5%B2-%E9%A9%9A%E9%9A%AA%E4%B8%80%E5%88%BB%E4%BF%9D%E5%AE%89%E4%BA%BA%E5%93%A1%E7%94%A8%E4%BB%80%E9%BA%BC%E4%BF%9D%E8%AD%B7%E9%A6%AC%E6%9D%9C%E7%BE%85\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2F219036%2F%25E5%25A4%259A%25E5%259C%2596-%25E5%25A7%2594%25E5%2585%25A7%25E7%2591%259E%25E6%258B%2589%25E7%25B8%25BD%25E7%25B5%25B1%25E5%258F%2597%25E8%25A5%25B2-%25E9%25A9%259A%25E9%259A%25AA%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%2588%25BB%25E4%25BF%259D%25E5%25AE%2589%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2593%25A1%25E7%2594%25A8%25E4%25BB%2580%25E9%25BA%25BC%25E4%25BF%259D%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E6%259D%259C%25E7%25BE%2585&d=b%2FhkngfqhQp5uMDeYX4ms1eK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=e59871de\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/219036/%E5%A4%9A%E5%9C%96-%E5%A7%94%E5%85%A7%E7%91%9E%E6%8B%89%E7%B8%BD%E7%B5%B1%E5%8F%97%E8%A5%B2-%E9%A9%9A%E9%9A%AA%E4%B8%80%E5%88%BB%E4%BF%9D%E5%AE%89%E4%BA%BA%E5%93%A1%E7%94%A8%E4%BB%80%E9%BA%BC%E4%BF%9D%E8%AD%B7%E9%A6%AC%E6%9D%9C%E7%BE%85</a>"},{"pid":"58b79797bcbc12a196fc32170dab996a562eb2b0","tid":768968,"uid":29080,"like":0